r"""
CESMLC V7.1 Standalone Hybrid Anomaly Detector
===============================================

This is a full standalone version. It does not import V6/V7 code.

Core design
-----------
1. Candidate gate: latest-day DB_MISMATCH='YES'.
2. Evidence window: 30/35-day SOURCE history for candidate ECGIs only.
3. Signature engine: deterministic rules for known CESMLC/RAN anomaly signatures.
4. Unsupervised engine: global + feature-wise IsolationForest on engineered history metrics.
5. Fusion layer: combines rule signatures and unsupervised outlier evidence into:
      PRIMARY_ANOMALY_CLUSTER
      PRIMARY_ABNORMAL_FEATURE
      ANOMALY_RISK_SCORE
      MODEL_SIGNATURE_AGREEMENT
6. Outputs: ML-ready/labeling data, clustered final top-100 report, top-30 per cluster,
   abnormal days/amounts, ECGI evidence bullets, lat/lon movement distance, cache diagnostics, and visual storytelling plots.

Install once if needed:
    python -m pip install duckdb pandas numpy scikit-learn matplotlib

Typical run:
    python cesmlc_v71_standalone_seed_label_dataset_builder.py ^
